{"tid":518088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳PayPal創辦人都係Fans！Bitcoin曾重返1.5萬美元","createTime":"2018-01-03T03:28:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T03:31:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f19e8345a5ebeabffc5160a329a96a35204da070","tid":518088,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180103/large/1514947814_4abd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180103%2Flarge%2F1514947814_4abd.jpg&h=d24c59bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBitcoin去年雖然狂升13倍，但不少人對其投資價值有所懷疑，甚至有多名美國前官員均在公開場合警告，Bitcoin最終會一文值。但它仍然有不少支持者，包括PayPal聯合創辦人Peter Thiel旗下的Founders Fund。<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》引述消息人士透露，Founders Fund購入1500至2000萬美元比特幣，至今價值已達到數億美元，而這個投資決定則是Thiel與Founders其他投資合伙人共同作出的決定。<br />\n事實上Thiel早在去年10月接受採訪時已經提到，加密貨幣極有魅力，並且認為有些人低估了比特幣，因為比特幣就像一種儲備貨幣。而Founders亦向投資者表示，比特幣是高風險、高回報的投資，而比特幣則可能於未來幾年上漲數倍。<br />\n<br />\n不過，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">Founders亦警告投資，比特幣最後可能變得一文不值，或者幾乎一文不值。<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n在<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">傳出Founders持有比特幣消息傳出後</span></span></strong>，比特幣昨晚即抽升，並重返1.4萬美元水平，高見15,274美元；最新報14,789美元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742c7c033e5c41e4ddcef9a70bf8fd1a0befa726","tid":518088,"uid":122264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:30:20.000Z","msg":"吹完風之後all out"},{"pid":"ad1d74045ac5eab760574b079825628ddc20ccbf","tid":518088,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"742c7c033e5c41e4ddcef9a70bf8fd1a0befa726","tid":518088,"uid":122264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:30:20.000Z","msg":"吹完風之後all out"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:31:20.000Z","msg":"唔識字?<br />\n<br />\n一邊吹淡, 一邊all in呀"}]}